### 4. Core Features Implemented

#### Bilingual Support
- English/Hindi UI language toggle
- Agent responds in selected language
- Language preference persisted in localStorage

#### Chat History & User Management
- Auto-generated unique user IDs
- Session-based conversations
- localStorage persistence for all chat data
- Conversation metadata tracking
- View, load, and delete past conversations
- Up to 50 conversations retained per user

#### Markdown Rendering
- Custom markdown formatter (no external dependencies)
- Supports: bold, italic, inline code, numbered lists, headings
- Proper HTML rendering with security considerations

#### Responsive Design
- Mobile: Hamburger menu, full-width overlay sidebar
- Desktop: Fixed-width sidebar (320px), history icon toggle
- Breakpoints: sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px)
- Responsive typography and spacing

#### Theme System
- Light mode (default)
- Dark mode toggle
- Professional orange accent colors
- Proper semantic color tokens
- No hydration flash

#### Information Source Tracking
- Knowledge Base badge (green, Database icon)
- Web Search badge (blue, Globe icon)
- Combined badges when both sources used
- Visual feedback on data origin

