### 6. Technical Specifications

**Data Persistence:**
- `impact_saathi_user_id` - User identifier
- `impact_saathi_language` - Language preference (en/hi)
- `impact_saathi_conversations` - Conversation metadata array
- `impact_saathi_chat_{sessionId}` - Individual conversation messages

**Agent Integration:**
- Uses `/app/nextjs-project/lib/aiAgent.ts` for all AI interactions
- Passes user_id and session_id with each request
- Language instruction appended to messages for Hindi responses
- JSON parsing with custom normalizer

**UI Patterns:**
- Custom markdown formatter
- Hydration-safe theme toggle
- Mobile-first responsive design
- ScrollArea for proper overflow handling
- Auto-scroll to latest message
- Typing indicator animation

